*Installation Procedure for mp3act*
The goal of mp3act is to make listening to music as easy as possible.  The installation of mp3act is just as easy. Here's what you do:

* Download a copy mp3act
* Uncompress the archive into a new directory in your webserver root
* Create a new MySQL Database.  Something like _mp3act_
* Edit the mp3act.conf file in the includes/ directory and fill in the database parameters
* Point your browser to the install page (ex. http://yourserver.com/mp3act/install.php)
* Follow the steps to install.
* Thats It!

*You may also need to do the following*
* set the permissions of your audio device to be writable by the apache user
* set the _allow_url_fopen = On_ in your php.ini file